    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The mechanical integrity is absolute; both the rod bearings and rear subframe have been proactively reinforced to exceed factory standards. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring surgical cornering exits. With a flawless chassis, factory-spec compression across all cylinders, and an untouched aesthetic, this example offers a pure, visceral driving experience that remains as sharp as the day it left Regensburg.",
