      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle preserved in absolute showroom condition. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, showing zero signs of wear on its flawless factory finish. The exterior gleams with a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'time-capsule' state; the premium leather upholstery is taut and pristine, with no creases or scuffs to be found. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a fully documented service history from certified specialists and exceptionally low mileage. This is a collector-grade example for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection. Complete with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title.",
