      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, strictly garage-kept and pampered since day one. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s essentially brand new without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look and see for yourself, it\u2019s a total dream!",
